data.description: Inviting single-level home with classic touches is now on the market! This 3-bed, 2-bath property beckons with its cozy front porch, an ideal spot to relax with a morning coffee. Upon entering, you're greeted by a perfectly sized living room, allowing just enough space for relaxation. Adjacent to the living room is the formal dining room w/a brick-accented fireplace, creating warmth during cooler months & a charming backdrop for dinner parties. Impeccable kitchen boasts white cabinets, tile backsplash, granite counters, SS appliances, a wine cooler, & a breakfast bar. Continue to the main bedroom, showcasing a private bathroom for convenience. The lovely backyard has a covered patio, the perfect shaded area for leisurely afternoons. What are you waiting for? Visit right now!
